<p>消失螢光幕多年的梁細妹，原來早已退休，在家含飴弄孫。大兒子Robert十年如一日的不務實，常幻想能一步登天，使梁細妹把自己的希望完全寄託在小兒子Albert身上而對他疼愛有加。此舉卻讓Robert認為母親偏心，誓言一定要發大財來換取母親對自己的重視。機緣巧合之下，Robert獲得一尊財神婆的玩偶公仔，財神婆更現出真身與他交流，希望他能以正道獲取財富。Robert自以為財運已到而不斷的想依靠邪門歪道試圖一夜致富。囂張的行徑，招致了破財神出現，令Robert陷入萬劫不復的局面，抵押房子以及高利貸借來的款項，一夜之間化為烏有。這次真的是…傷腦筋哦！<\/p>","vod_play_from":"snm3u8","vod_play_server":"no","vod_play_note":"","vod_play_url":"HD$https:\/\/v5.rstu6.com\/202408\/09\/weYbRaMyx47\/video\/index.m3u8","vod_down_from":"","vod_down_server":"","vod_down_note":"","vod_down_url":"","vod_plot":0,"vod_plot_name":"","vod_plot_detail":"","type_name":"喜剧片"},{"vod_id":149491,"type_id":7,"type_id_1":1,"group_id":0,"vod_name":"戏曲小子","vod_sub":"Wayang Boy","vod_en":"xiquxiaozi","vod_status":1,"vod_letter":"X","vod_color":"","vod_tag":"","vod_class":"新加坡,喜剧","vod_pic":"https:\/\/snzypic.vip\/upload\/vod\/20260628-1\/66e79ade7e5a5a7da73293fb27f991ec.jpg","vod_pic_thumb":"","vod_pic_slide":"","vod_pic_screenshot":"","vod_actor":"罗家英,刘香慈","vod_director":"Raymond·Tan","vod_writer":"","vod_behind":"","vod_blurb":"暂无剧情简介","vod_remarks":"HD国语","vod_pubdate":"2014-11-13","vod_total":0,"vod_serial":"0","vod_tv":"","vod_weekday":"","vod_area":"新加坡","vod_lang":"汉语普通话","vod_year":"2014","vod_version":"","vod_state":"正片","vod_author":"豆瓣","vod_jumpurl":"","vod_tpl":"","vod_tpl_play":"","vod_tpl_down":"","vod_isend":0,"vod_lock":0,"vod_level":0,"vod_copyright":0,"vod_points":0,"vod_points_play":0,"vod_points_down":0,"vod_hits":96,"vod_hits_day":223,"vod_hits_week":293,"vod_hits_month":264,"vod_duration":"100分钟","vod_up":629,"vod_down":663,"vod_score":"10.0","vod_score_all":2460,"vod_score_num":246,"vod_time":"2026-06-28 14:50:48","vod_time_add":1782629355,"vod_time_hits":0,"vod_time_make":0,"vod_trysee":0,"vod_douban_id":26691153,"vod_douban_score":"0.0","vod_reurl":"","vod_rel_vod":"","vod_rel_art":"","vod_pwd":"","vod_pwd_url":"","vod_pwd_play":"","vod_pwd_play_url":"","vod_pwd_down":"","vod_pwd_down_url":"","vod_content":"<p>暂无剧情简介<\/p>","vod_play_from":"snm3